{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775885793828,"sessionID":"ses_284f6021cffeTAzasD9m8U9pO5","part":{"id":"prt_d7b0a9b2d001ZTRVCraFGVYXBB","messageID":"msg_d7b0a8d67001Udh8wV6GcKmOjT","sessionID":"ses_284f6021cffeTAzasD9m8U9pO5","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_16cf5da27b2f48caacde4a7a","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# Delta Spec: AR-042 — Docusaurus 文档站框架\n\n## Overview\n\nThis delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for implementing the Docusaurus documentation site framework for the agentcube project.\n\n## Base Specifications\n\n- **AR**: AR-042\n- **Module**: `docs`\n- **Language**: TypeScript\n- **Size**: M\n- **Base Spec**: TBD\n\n---\n\n## Scenario: Project Initialization\n\n### AR-042-001: Initialize Docusaurus project\n\n- **GIVEN** a new docs module requirement\n- **WHEN** initializing a Docusaurus project\n- **THEN** it SHALL use TypeScript for type safety\n- **AND** SHALL follow the standard Docusaurus project structure\n\n### AR-042-002: Dependency configuration\n\n- **GIVEN** package.json configuration\n- **WHEN** setting up dependencies\n- **THEN** it SHALL include docusaurus package\n- **AND** SHALL include necessary TypeScript types\n\n---\n\n## Scenario: Documentation Structure\n\n### AR-042-003: Documentation directory structure\n\n- **GIVEN** Docusaurus project\n- **WHEN** organizing documentation\n- **THEN** it SHALL have proper docs directory layout\n- **AND** SHALL include sidebar configuration\n\n### AR-042-004: Custom components\n\n- **GIVEN** documentation site\n- **WHEN** extending Docusaurus\n- **THEN** it SHALL support custom React components\n- **AND** SHALL include proper TypeScript typing\n\n---\n\n## Scenario: Build and Deployment\n\n### AR-042-005: Build configuration\n\n- **GIVEN** Docusaurus project\n- **WHEN** configuring build process\n- **THEN** it SHALL produce optimized static files\n- **AND** SHALL support multiple output formats\n\n### AR-042-006: Version documentation\n\n- **GIVEN** documentation site\n- **WHEN** managing versions\n- **THEN** it SHALL support documentation versioning\n- **AND** SHALL maintain versioned docs properly\n\n---\n\n## References\n\n- Docusaurus: https://docusaurus.io/\n- TypeScript: https://www.typescriptlang.org/","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-042/delta-spec.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-042/delta-spec.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-042/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775885793816,"end":1775885793825}}}}
